instant inspiration i am about to begin my first year teaching high school art , and this book has sparked more excitement for the career i have chosen than any other . i expect to return to it again and again when i need a pick-me-up during my upcoming `` difficult first year '' of teaching - it makes me feel lucky to be able to be in the field of education . any teacher , novice or experienced , would find inspiration in this wonderfully easy to read and engaging book on meaningful teaching